### Kafka Pulse Demo API Requests

### Health Check Endpoints

# General health status
GET http://localhost:8888/health
Accept: application/json

### Consumer Control Endpoints

# Get current consumer status
GET http://localhost:8888/control/status
Accept: application/json

###

# Trigger consumer group rebalance
POST http://localhost:8888/control/rebalance
Content-Type: application/json

###

# Pause consumer - simulates stuck consumer behavior
POST http://localhost:8888/control/pause
Content-Type: application/json

###

# Resume consumer - recovers from stuck state
POST http://localhost:8888/control/resume  
Content-Type: application/json

###

# Set slow processing - simulates slow consumer with 10 second delay
POST http://localhost:8888/control/slow
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "delay": "10s"
}